eventText: Pranav has asked Mariona to send the design draft for ESMO app.

Rahul sends links of 13 tools to Constance. Constance will forward it to the client.

Constance has informed that client is not fixated on 30 April deadline.
The Management of IR guideline is on CMS.
Management of Toxicities GL is now on CMS.
Sambhaji creates a new account for ESMO, bbteamesmo@gmail.com. Sambhaji sends this email to Constance and Sylvia for adding bbteamesmo@gmail.com and remove kapil.lokhande@media4u.com.
